high_descs: Turn left and walk six steps, turn right for one step and then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave door and put the knife in the wine glass.
Take the wine glass, with the knife still in it, out and shut the door.
Turn around and walk to the counter ahead, turn left and face the counter by the sink.
Put the wine glass down on the counter to your right.
anns.task_desc: Put a wine glass with a knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the sink, then turn right and walk up to the counter, after that turn left and look down at the counter.
Pick up the butter knife off of the counter.
Turn left and walk over to the microwave on the counter.
Open the microwave and put the butter knife handle down in the glass that is in the microwave.
Pick up the glass with the butter knife in it out of the microwave and close the microwave.
Turn around and walk over to the counter, then turn left.
Put the glass with the knife in it on the front edge of the counter to your right.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a butter knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go across the room to the sink.
Pick up the knife on the right side of the sink.
Turn left and go to the microwave.
Put the knife in the glass in the microwave.
Pick up the glass in the microwave.
Turn around go back to the sink.
Put the glass on the counter to the far right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in a glass on the counter.
